## Open Questions

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **1. Stripe Account:** Do you already have a Stripe account and API keys? If not, Phase 3 international payments will need to be deferred.

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **2. R2 (Cloudflare):** Do you have R2 credentials configured? Phase 6 depends on this. If not, we can use the existing local/S3 storage as a fallback.

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **3. Embedding Model:** For Phase 6 PDF indexing, which embedding model should we use? Options: OpenAI `text-embedding-3-small` (~$0.02/1M tokens), or a local model via Ollama.

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **4. OpenRouter Cost API:** OpenRouter provides per-request cost in the `x-openrouter-cost` response header. Should we rely on this for real-time cost tracking, or maintain our own static pricing table as a fallback?

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **5. Execution Order:** I recommend executing **Phases 1→2→4→3→5→6**. Phase 4 (UI) can be done in parallel with Phase 2 (backend credits). Phase 6 (PDF) can be deferred. Do you agree with this order?

